            <lg xml:id="TK350">
<l>paṟṟuka paṟṟaṟṟāṉ paṟṟiṉai yappaṟṟaip</l>
<l>paṟṟuka paṟṟu viṭaṟku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Desire the desire of Him who is without desire; in order to renounce desire, desire that desire.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
